caption: Right when I walked in, I was greeted by a barista while he was making drinks for other customers. While I waited in line, a man cut in front of me. I don’t think he realized I was in line because of social distancing, and I’m a doormat so I wasn’t gonna say anything lol but the barista noticed I was there first and politely explained that to the man. My latte was awesome and the staff was so kind here! :)

Best, cleanest, fastest, most accurate and consistent Starbucks I’ve ever been to. These guys deserve major recognition, especially the night crew who are always so cheerful, respectful and great in every sense. The music is also amazing and a major reason why I love coming back every day! Love the playlist! Shoutout to my guys at night: K. Naim, Anael, Nick, and Josh...sorry if I’ve missed anybody else, but you know who you are! I wouldn’t be here without these guys. Thank you fellas! Keep up the good work.

The most clean, organized and well maintained Starbucks I’ve been to in the world besides the reserve stores. Very quick, and precise service. They are always stocked up and have the products I want. I’m happy to write a 5-star review for this place and all of the employees working there because they deserve it. Thank you to all for your amazing service. Special shout-out to K. Naim. One of the most humble people I met. He always greets me, remembers my drink, and always makes it correctly. I’ve never experienced such consistency with my drink like I have when he makes it. He makes it correct every time, exactly how I want it, and with love! This young man deserves a promotion! Such a wonderful and professional individual. You will never notice a different or worse attitude from this young man. This is how it’s done!! All in all, thank you all! Love this Starbucks location.

Out of all the Starbucks stores in this city this is by far my favorite one, not only because of its close proximity to my workplace but because of how efficient they are. My favorite days are when the barista Karim is there, super courteous, clean environment, and always remembers my orders( attention to detail is awesome) . My drinks are ALWAYS made exactly how I place them even if I’ve customized it. KARIM might not know , or maybe he does I’m always raving how it really helps get my day off to a great start! Thank you for your hard work during this pandemic!

This starbucks is the worst. Ordered a cold brew with cascara foam and they took forever making it. I literally stood there watching him make it and he was like watching my drink to see the "foam go down." I heard him literally say out loud "Why isn't the foam going down?" Then he scrapped it off the top with the lid and put that lid on. So now I'm stuck with this cold brew with foam dripping down the sides. I taste it and it tasts SO BAD. I've ordered this drink before and it has never tasted like this. I saw the same guy who was making my drink make the order before mine and he opened the honey packets with his teeth. Then after putting the honey in the drink he put the packets back into his mouth to suck on the rest while making my drink. The last time I ordered the Nitro cold brew with cascara foam at another location, they put on top like a brown sugar powder on top, which of course this guy did not do. So I tried adding my own where the sugar and napkins are and of course nothing is stocked and everything is super dirty. Also, I've been to this Starbucks location before when I put in a mobile order for A TALL BLONDE and I waited like 15 mins before I got so fed up I asked the worker about it and they said that their machine that takes mobile orders has been broken. Like, who is the manager of this location anyways?
